# sonycam

This repo is **sonycam**: a Python CLI for Sony Alpha cameras over USB PC Remote (Alpha Camera REST API / CameraWebApp).

## Skills (read when relevant)

- Camera ops / REC / pull / liveview: [.cursor/skills/sonycam/SKILL.md](../skills/sonycam/SKILL.md)
- Changing code / build / OSS hygiene: [.cursor/skills/sonycam-dev/SKILL.md](../skills/sonycam-dev/SKILL.md)

## Defaults

- Install with `make install` (venv + editable)
- Master footage = in-camera REC + `pull`, never liveview JPEGs
- Prefer `127.0.0.1:8080` over `localhost`
- No camera serials or personal absolute paths in committed docs
- Update CLI help + README + skills when UX changes
